snippet.title: How Amber Heard Ruined Her Own Career
snippet.description:
Watch How Amber Heard Ruined Her Own Career 

Subscribe to Viral Network  👉 https://youtube.com/user/zrul90

Johnny Depp’s fans are probably cringing in the back at the fact that we made this video. Amber Heard started her career in 2003 quite steadily. But now she’s having trouble keeping her roles and being cast in movies. 
When she does get cast, she only has small forgettable roles. This is surprising, considering that the actress is quite attractive and definitely has an appeal. She should have fans, right?
What went wrong in her career, and can she fix it? Let's find out!
The actress that began her career in 2003, saw her ratings improve during her married years. She got big films like Magic Mike XXL, Danish Girl, and Adderall Diaries. She was also cast on television.
